{"id":184537,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/上海地铁删致歉微博引发公众愤怒/","date":"2011-09-29T19:30:25Z","modified":"2011-09-29T19:30:25Z","title":"上海地铁删致歉微博引发公众愤怒","content":"<p>昨天下午14时，上海地铁10号线发生了两列车追尾事故。运营商上海申通地铁官方微博迅速发布了一则致歉的帖子，“今天是上海地铁运营有史以来最黯淡的一天，无论最终原因和责任怎样，给市民乘客造成的伤害和损失尤感愧疚。再多致歉比起实际损害也显苍白，但还是要深深道歉。”该贴很快被删除，几小时后上海地铁发布了一则措辞正面的微博，呼吁用户“相信我们，一定会做好的！””。一时间引发了公众的愤怒。最后，这则微博也被神秘地删除了。然后，到晚上八点左右，道歉帖子再次公布了出来（截图）。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/18e868c1/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%9C%B0%E9%93%81%E5%88%A0%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E6%84%A4%E6%80%92&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F09%2F28%2F0825215%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%9C%B0%E9%93%81%E5%88%A0%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E6%84%A4%E6%80%92&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F09%2F28%2F0825215%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/114252244879/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/18e868c1/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/114252244879/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/18e868c1/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=Uxp7Mbi8j9Q:bbklAMGngOY:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=Uxp7Mbi8j9Q:bbklAMGngOY:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKB